testsuite.name: st.amnesty.OverridesHandlerSpec

testcase.name: get request with matching etag returns 304
get request with no Etag and correct service name returns 200 and overrides json
get request with un-matched service name returns 200
post request with malformed body returns 422
post request with improper type arguments returns 422
delete request with found service name returns 204
delete request with not found service name returns 404
